   - Added try-catch blocks with proper error propagation
   - Added more detailed logging of errors
   - Added stack trace printing for better debugging

4. **Added Message Broadcasting**:
   - Ensured that messages are broadcast to all clients, including the sender
   - Used both annotation-based and direct message sending for redundancy

